183f9a3ab05d83f6796a4de1fb","tid":1411963,"uid":105995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T05:13:02.000Z","msg":"退一步激化中國派系鬥爭 民間鬥爭 <br />\n<br />\n對香港都百利而無一害<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bf50e1ca2ed2e3f4be95d515db542b2f32df4ff","tid":1411963,"uid":222605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T05:13:16.000Z","msg":"Good idea<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2dbfad38245f9b5db074890dee26dadcbab4fd64","tid":1411963,"uid":105995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T05:22:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />文宣組準備"},{"pid":"0709d8f8ae4ef8b2d82b22130e47968e1b95dac7","tid":1411963,"uid":105995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T05:43:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aeb2a10a9874b7d7d4185b1be6bd6dd11697531f","tid":1411963,"uid":264771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T05:44:59.000Z","msg":"應該先主力向上海人宣傳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94b564c58e3a24dacb1ad57e9facbb7cac4dfe90","tid":1411963,"uid":131887,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T06:28:36.000Z","msg":"我個人嚟講覺得搞好我地香港呢邊就得，中國點關我地撚事咩。<br />\n<br />\n但係如果真係要搞中國文宣，我建議最好focus係令佢地內亂，增加政府維穩成本，而唔係要佢地支持香港。中國人有個特色就係道德水平特別低，你好難令佢哋犧牲自己，去支持同自己無關嘅香港人。尤其是中國人月入一萬已經屬於中產，佢地好撚葡萄香港人架，見到香港亂只會覺得香港人抵死，佢地不知幾想香港人仆街。同佢地講香港人要自由，佢地聽唔明架。<br />\n<br />\n所以最好由中國自己嘅嘢去入手，老實講我覺得可以由個人信用系統同網絡實名制導致個人私隱洩漏到入手煽動一下恐慌情緒，要燒到埋身啲人先識驚架。"},{"pid":"db5ab948cefbcffa99bd7df40d8baf9dd22842b5","tid":1411963,"uid":105995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T07:02:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afa44558d748cab2f6f43f0864271178b9efaf3a","tid":1411963,"uid":105995,"like":3,"dislike":0,"sc